    <section id="notes" class="- topic/section " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/user-guide/reference/r_exit-codes.dita" xtrc="section:1;58:25">
      <title class="- topic/title " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/user-guide/reference/r_exit-codes.dita" xtrc="title:3;59:14">Notes</title>
      <ul class="- topic/ul " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/user-guide/reference/r_exit-codes.dita" xtrc="ul:1;60:11">
        <li class="- topic/li " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/user-guide/reference/r_exit-codes.dita" xtrc="li:1;61:13">Suggested-level failures do not change the exit code. A file with
        only Suggested failures exits with code <codeph class="+ topic/ph pr-d/codeph " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/user-guide/reference/r_exit-codes.dita" xtrc="codeph:5;62:57">0</codeph>.</li>
        <li class="- topic/li " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/user-guide/reference/r_exit-codes.dita" xtrc="li:2;63:13">A parse error (file has no front matter) produces exit code
        <codeph class="+ topic/ph pr-d/codeph " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/user-guide/reference/r_exit-codes.dita" xtrc="codeph:6;64:17">1</codeph>. The file is counted as a failed scan.</li>
        <li class="- topic/li " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/user-guide/reference/r_exit-codes.dita" xtrc="li:3;65:13">In a directory scan, one failing file sets the exit code to
        <codeph class="+ topic/ph pr-d/codeph " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/user-guide/reference/r_exit-codes.dita" xtrc="codeph:7;66:17">1</codeph> for the entire run.</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section id="check-exit-code" class="- topic/section " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/user-guide/reference/r_exit-codes.dita" xtrc="section:2;70:35">
      <title class="- topic/title " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/user-guide/reference/r_exit-codes.dita" xtrc="title:4;71:14">Checking the exit code in a shell script</title>
      <codeblock xml:space="preserve" class="+ topic/pre pr-d/codeblock " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/user-guide/reference/r_exit-codes.dita" xtrc="codeblock:1;72:39">md-validate validate docs/ --rules rules/tutorial.json
if [ $? -eq 0 ]; then
  echo "All required rules passed."
else
  echo "Validation failed. Check the report for details."
